{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "caremind-ai-mvp-collection",
    "name": "CareMind AI — MVP API",
    "description": "End-to-end API collection for CareMind AI backend.\n\n**Recommended order**\n1. **1. Auth → Register Organization** — creates org, tenant DB, admin; saves tokens\n2. **2. Users (Admin) → Invite Doctor** (admin token)\n3. **1. Auth → Login (Doctor)** — set `doctorPassword` from invite email (Mailhog :8025)\n4. **2b. Users (Doctor) → Invite Patient** (doctor token) *or* **2. Invite Patient (Admin)**\n5. **1. Auth → Login (Patient)** — set `patientPassword` from invite email\n6. **3. Appointments** — create, consent (patient token)\n7. **4–8** — consultations, documents, AI, outputs, PDF, admin\n\n**Variables:** `baseUrl`, `accessToken`, `doctorAccessToken`, `patientAccessToken`, `doctorId`, `patientId`, etc.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "doctorAccessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "patientAccessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "orgSlug", "value": "demo-clinic" },
    { "key": "adminEmail", "value": "admin@demo.clinic" },
    { "key": "adminPassword", "value": "SecurePass123!" },
    { "key": "doctorEmail", "value": "doctor@demo.clinic" },
    { "key": "doctorPassword", "value": "" },
    { "key": "patientEmail", "value": "patient@demo.clinic" },
    { "key": "patientPassword", "value": "" },
    { "key": "doctorId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "patientId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "appointmentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "documentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "aiOutputId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "tempMfaToken", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1. Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Organization",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data?.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken);",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"orgName\": \"Demo Clinic\",\n  \"orgSlug\": \"{{orgSlug}}\",\n  \"adminEmail\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"adminPassword\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register-org"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data?.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken);",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Doctor)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data?.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('doctorAccessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "}",
                  "if (json.data?.requiresMfa) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('tempMfaToken', json.data.tempToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{doctorEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{doctorPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Patient)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data?.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('patientAccessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{patientEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{patientPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data?.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "MFA Setup",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/mfa/setup"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "MFA Confirm Setup",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"000000\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/mfa/confirm-setup"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "MFA Verify (after login requiresMfa)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"000000\",\n  \"tempToken\": \"{{tempMfaToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/mfa/verify"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Users (Admin)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Invite Doctor",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data?.doctorId) pm.collectionVariables.set('doctorId', json.data.doctorId);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{doctorEmail}}\",\n  \"firstName\": \"Jane\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Smith\",\n  \"specialty\": \"General Practice\",\n  \"licenseNumber\": \"MD-12345\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/invite-doctor"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Invite Patient (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data?.patientId) pm.collectionVariables.set('patientId', json.data.patientId);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{patientEmail}}\",\n  \"firstName\": \"John\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Doe\",\n  \"phone\": \"+15551234567\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/invite-patient"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Users",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "users"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete User",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/:userId",
            "variable": [{ "key": "userId", "value": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" }]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2b. Users (Doctor)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Invite Patient (Doctor)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data?.patientId) pm.collectionVariables.set('patientId', json.data.patientId);",
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{doctorAccessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{patientEmail}}\",\n  \"firstName\": \"John\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Doe\",\n  \"phone\": \"+15551234567\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/invite-patient"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Appointments",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Appointment",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('appointmentId', json.data.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"patientId\": \"{{patientId}}\",\n  \"doctorId\": \"{{doctorId}}\",\n  \"scheduledAt\": \"2026-12-01T10:00:00.000Z\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/appointments"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Appointments",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/appointments?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "appointments"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Appointment",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Appointment",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"in_progress\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Record Consent (Patient)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{patientAccessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"consentStatus\": \"accepted\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/consent"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Cancel Appointment",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Consultations",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Join Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{patientAccessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/consultations/{{appointmentId}}/join-token"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Start Recording",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{doctorAccessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/consultations/{{appointmentId}}/recording/start"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Stop Recording",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{doctorAccessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/consultations/{{appointmentId}}/recording/stop"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Transcript",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{doctorAccessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/consultations/{{appointmentId}}/transcript"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get AI Outputs",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{doctorAccessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/consultations/{{appointmentId}}/outputs"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Documents",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload Document",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('documentId', json.data.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "file", "type": "file", "src": [] },
                { "key": "patientId", "value": "{{patientId}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "documentType", "value": "lab_report", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/documents/upload",
            "description": "Select a PDF, JPG, or PNG file in the form-data `file` field before sending."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Documents",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/documents?page=1&limit=20&patientId={{patientId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "documents"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "patientId", "value": "{{patientId}}" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Document",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Document",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "6. AI Assistant",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Chat",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{patientAccessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"message\": \"What medications were discussed in my last visit?\",\n  \"appointmentId\": \"{{appointmentId}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Chat Stream (SSE)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{patientAccessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"message\": \"Summarize my recent lab results in simple terms.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat/stream"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Doctor Copilot",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{doctorAccessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ai/doctor-copilot/{{patientId}}?q=What should I review before this patient's follow-up?",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "ai", "doctor-copilot", "{{patientId}}"],
              "query": [{ "key": "q", "value": "What should I review before this patient's follow-up?" }]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "7. AI Outputs (Doctor)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List by Appointment",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "const outputs = json.data;",
                  "if (Array.isArray(outputs) && outputs[0]?.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('aiOutputId', outputs[0].id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{doctorAccessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ai-outputs/appointment/{{appointmentId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Approve Output",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{doctorAccessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"editedContent\": \"Optional edited text for the patient summary.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ai-outputs/{{aiOutputId}}/approve"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reject Output",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{doctorAccessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ai-outputs/{{aiOutputId}}/reject"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Output History",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{doctorAccessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ai-outputs/{{aiOutputId}}/history"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "8. PDF Export",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Visit Summary PDF",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{patientAccessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/pdf-export/visit-summary/{{appointmentId}}",
            "description": "Requires an approved `patient_summary` AI output for the appointment."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "9. Admin",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Dashboard",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Audit Logs",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit-logs?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "audit-logs"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Recent Activity",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/activity"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
